      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "New here? Have a seat, don't be nervous. I'm the... temporary head of this Interstellar Assignment Bureau.",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Do you know the Galaxy Human Resources Department?",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 4,
          "speakerName": null,
          "text": null,
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "Know",
              "nextNodeId": 2
            },
            {
              "text": "Don't know",
              "nextNodeId": 3
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 0
    },
    "2": {
      "dialogueId": 2,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Great. Simply put, recently a group of alien 'job seekers' have flooded in. They've grown tired of their own planets and want to work in a different place.",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 4
    },
    "3": {
      "dialogueId": 3,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "It doesn't matter if you don't know. Anyway, they only send emails.",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "In short, recently there has been a wave of alien \"job seekers\" pouring in. They've grown tired of staying on their own planets and want to work in a different place.",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 4
    },
    "4": {
      "dialogueId": 4,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "But the problem is, some of those extraterrestrial beings have good temperaments, some have an IQ comparable to a rock, and some...",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Well, Colleague Aichi.",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Our job is to test them and then assign them to the appropriate planets.",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "If everything is correct, you'll also receive a wonderful surprise gift from headquarters!",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Next, your senior colleague Wang Jiang will guide you in learning basic assignment knowledge.",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "All in all, work hard, young man. Ciao~!",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 0
    },
    "5": {
      "dialogueId": 5,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Oh, it seems you've completed your first day of work~",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Let me take a look at your completion report.",
          "choices": null
        },
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "n super satisfied, n average, n complaints and negative reviews!",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 0
    },
    "6": {
      "dialogueId": 6,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "It seems you're quite perceptive!",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 10
    },
    "7": {
      "dialogueId": 7,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "It seems you're very serious~",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 10
    },
    "8": {
      "dialogueId": 8,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "It seems you still have something to learn~",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 10
    },
    "9": {
      "dialogueId": 9,
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": 0,
          "speakerName": "HR Manager",
          "text": "Oh my god! Do you think with your toes?!",
          "choices": null
        }
      ],
      "nextDialogueId": 10
    },
    "10": {
      "dialogueId": 10,
      "lines": [
